com.kontakt.sdk.android.ble.filter.eddystone

Interface EddystoneFilter

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.android.internal.util.Predicate<IEddystoneDevice>

    public interface EddystoneFilter
extends com.android.internal.util.Predicate<IEddystoneDevice>
    Filters are designed to enable more detailed devices search and thus reduce battery consumption. Predicate accepting Eddystone's specific UID advertising packet. The packet has the following structure:
    • [0]..[9] - namespace id bytes
    • [10]..[15] - instance id bytes
